node.text:
Words cannot express how much I love you and miss you, my #goldenstars ✨ We’ve seen each other grow through thick and thin. You’ve picked me up and given me the strength to continue this amazing journey. I couldn’t have done anything without you. Thank you! 14 years and counting😘 

Our journey continues…💫
#14YearsWithJessicaJung
